2 23 24 25 26 *27 28 29 30 31\nAvg. Hi\nAvg. Lo\nActual Hi\nActual Lo\nForecast Hi\nForecast Lo\n*Temporarily Unavailable \n## May Weather in Tokyo\nTokyo's May 2026 forecast shows daily high temperatures ranging from 26.2° to 32.1°, with overnight lows between 17.6° and 21.4°. The average high for May is 29° with an average low of 20°. AccuWeather's monthly forecast extends further ahead than any other source, with day-by-day [RealFeel® Temperatures](https://www.accuweather.com/en/weather-news/how-we-calculate-real-feel-temperatures/189005) giving a complete picture of how May weather will actually feel in Tokyo. See also: [June](https://www.accuweather.com/en/jp/tokyo/226396/june-weather/226396?year=2026) | [July](https://www.accuweather.com/en/jp/tokyo/226396/july-weather/226396?year=2026) | [August](https://www.accuweather.com/en/jp/tokyo/226396/august-weather/226396?year=2026). \nFurther Ahead\n### [June 2026 ](https://www.accuweather.com/en/jp/tokyo/226396/june-weather/226396?year=2026) ### [July 2026 ](https://www.accuweather.com/en/jp/tokyo/226396/july-weather/226396?year=2026) ### [August 2026 ](https://www.accuweather.com/en/jp/tokyo/226396/august-weather/226396?year=2026)\nAround the Globe\n### [Hurricane Tracker ](https://www.accuweather.com/en/hurricane) ### [Severe Weather ](https://www.accuweather.com/en/jp/severe-weather) ### [Radar & Maps ](https://www.accuweather.com/en/jp/tokyo/weather-radar) ### [News ](https://www.accuweather.com/en/weather-news) ### [Video ](https://www.accuweather.com/en/videos)\nTop Stories\n[ Weather Forecasts Summerlike midweek surge in Northeast to be chased by more chill 3 hours ago ](https://www.accuweather.com/en/weather-forecasts/summerlike-midweek-surge-in-northeast-to-be-chased-by-more-chill-even-snowflakes-this-weekend/1894809) [ Severe Weather Woman dies after vehicle is swept away in Mississippi flash flooding 1 day ago ](https://www.accuweather.com/en/severe-weather/woman-dies-after-vehicle-is-swept-away-in-missi